article.description: Jermaine Marrow had 22 points as Hampton topped NJIT 82-70 in the CollegeInsider.com Postseason Tournament quarterfinals on Thursday night.
article.headline: Marrow scores 22 to carry Hampton past NJIT 82-70
article.linkText: Marrow scores 22 to carry Hampton past NJIT 82-70
article.story: NEWARK, N.J. -- Jermaine Marrow had 22 points as Hampton topped NJIT 82-70 in the CollegeInsider.com Postseason Tournament quarterfinals on Thursday night. Greg Heckstall had 19 points for Hampton (18-16). Kalin Fisher added 16 points. Trevond Barnes had 13 points for the visiting team. Zach Cooks had 22 points for the Highlanders (22-13). Diandre Wilson added 12 points. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
